===Etymology===
{{Han compound|戈|口|一|ls=ic}}.

Note that [[咸]] is not derived from 或, and that the characters 口一 are stacked in the opposite order in these characters. Both are ultimately from {{term|戈||halberd, spear|sc=Hani}}.

